text: Regīna Ločmele-Luņova (born 1966) is a Latvian politician. She is a member of Harmony and a deputy of the 12th Saeima. ==References== Category:1966 births Category:Living people Category:People from Sevastopol Category:Social Democratic Party "Harmony" politicians Category:Deputies of the 12th Saeima Category:Deputies of the 13th Saeima Category:Women deputies of the Saeima Category:21st-century Latvian women politicians
title: Regīna Ločmele-Luņova
